Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夺走的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐被夺走的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓…子…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集“苍穹之战神”第23话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫掠 - 诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗？
